==Starting out==
===Talking to Lucien===
* '''Lucien:''' I seek a hero to go on an important mission!
* '''Player:''' I am a mighty hero!
* {{tcond|If the player's inventory is full:}}
** '''Lucien:''' I require the Staff of Armadyl. But if you wish to seek it for me, you must free up some inventory space so that I can give you what you need.
** {{tact|end}}
* '''Lucien:''' I require the Staff of Armadyl. It is in the deserted Temple of Ikov, near Hemenster, north east of here.
* '''Lucien:''' Take care hero! There is a dangerous monster somewhere in the temple!
* {{topt|Why can't you get it yourself?}}
** '''Player:''' Why can't you get it yourself?
** '''Lucien:''' The guardians of the Staff of Armadyl fear me!
** '''Lucien:''' They have set up a magical barrier which even my power cannot overcome!
** {{tbox|Before starting this quest, be aware that one or more of your skill levels are lower than what is required to fully complete it. Your combat level is also lower than the recommended level of 45.}}
** {{tselect|Start the Temple of Ikov quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' That sounds like a laugh!
*** '''Lucien:''' It's not as easy as it sounds. The monster can only be killed with a weapon of ice. There are many other dangers.
*** '''Player:''' I'm up for it!
*** '''Lucien:''' I shall give you a pendant. Without it you will not be able to enter the Chamber of Fear.
*** '''Lucien:''' Here is my pendant. Now, I cannot stay here much longer. Meet me in my house, across the river south-east from Edgeville. It is next to the so-called Grand Exchange.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'll pass this time.
*** '''Lucien:''' Hmph.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Whats the reward?!}}
** '''Player:''' What's the reward?
** '''Lucien:''' I see you are the mercenary type.
** '''Player:''' It's a living.
** '''Lucien:''' I will reward you well if you bring me the staff.
** {{tselect|Start the Temple of Ikov quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Oh no! Sounds far too dangerous!}}
** '''Player:''' Oh no! Sounds far too dangerous!
** '''Lucien:''' Wimp! Call yourself a hero?! My daughter is more of a hero than you!
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Lucien again===
* '''Lucien:''' I told you not to meet me here again! Soon I will go to my house, across the river south-east from Edgeville. It is next to the so-called Grand Exchange.
* {{tcond|If the player lost the pendant:}}
** '''Player:''' I've lost the pendant you gave me.
** '''Lucien:''' Imbecile!
** {{tbox|pic=Pendant of lucien detail.png|Lucien has given you another pendant!}} {{^|Drops to floor with full inventory.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player still has the pendant:}}
** '''Player:''' Sorry! Can you remind me of my mission?
** '''Lucien:''' My patience grows thin hero!
** '''Lucien:''' I need the Staff of Armadyl. It's in the Temple of Ikov, near Hemenster, north east of here.
** {{tact|end}}

==Inside the dungeon==
===Going downstairs without a light source===
* {{tbox|It's a bit dark down here! You decide not to venture far.}}
* {{tact|end}}

=== Opening the north gate without wearing a Pendant of Lucien ===
* {{tbox|As you reach to open the door a great terror overcomes you!}}
* {{tact|end}}

=== Opening the south Gate while it's still locked ===
* {{tbox|The door won't open!}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Crossing the bridge while too heavy===
* {{mes|The bridge gives way under your weight!}}
* '''Player:''' {{overhead|Ow! Hot! Hot!}}
* {{tact|The player is dealt 20 damage.}}
* {{mes|Good thing that lava was shallow!}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Using lever on lever bracket===
* {{tbox|You fit the lever into the bracket.}}
* {{tbox|You hear the clunking of some hidden machinery.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Search for traps lever===
* {{tcond|With 42 Thieving:}}
** {{tbox|You find a trap on the lever! You disable the trap.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|Without 42 Thieving:}}
** {{tbox|You find nothing.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Searching ice arrow chest===
* {{tcond|If the chest has arrows:}}
** {{tbox|pic=Ice arrows detail.png|You found some ice arrows!}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the chest is empty:}}
** {{mes|You search the chest, but find nothing.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Opening door in Fire warrior room===
* {{tact|Fire Warrior of Lesarkus spawns.}}
* '''Fire Warrior of Lesarkus:''' {{overhead|You will not pass!}}
* '''Fire Warrior of Lesarkus:''' {{overhead|Amitus! Setitii!}}
* {{tact|The Fire Warrior casts fire bolt and knocks the player back from the door.}}

===Trying to open the trapdoor southeast of Lesarkus===
* {{tbox|You try to open the trapdoor but it won't budge! It looks like the trapdoor can only be opened from the other side.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the Fire Warrior of Lesarkus===
* '''Fire Warrior of Lesarkus:''' Who dares to enter the Temple of Ikov!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|A mighty hero!}}
** '''Player:''' A mighty hero!
** '''Fire Warrior of Lesarkus:''' Pathetic fool! Prepare to die!
** {{tact|The Fire Warrior attacks.}}
* {{topt|A humble pilgrim.}}
** '''Player:''' A humble pilgrim.
** '''Fire Warrior of Lesarkus:''' I haven't seen a pilgrim for thousands of years!
** '''Fire Warrior of Lesarkus:''' Temple is closed!
** {{tact|end}}

===Attacking the Fire Warrior of Lesarkus without ice arrows===
* '''Fire Warrior of Lesarkus:''' Your puny weapons do nothing against me human! Come back when you can give me a real fight!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Winelda===
* '''Winelda:''' Hehe! We see you're in a pickle!
* '''Winelda:''' Wants to be getting over the nasty lava do we?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Nah, not bothered!}}
** '''Player:''' Nah, not bothered!
** '''Winelda:''' Hehe! Ye'll come back! They always come back!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Yes we do!}}
** '''Player:''' Yes we do!
** '''Winelda:''' Mocking us are we? Clever one aren't we?
** '''Winelda:''' I'm knowing some magic trickesses! I could get over easy as that!
** '''Winelda:''' Don't tell them! They always come! They pester poor Winelda!
** '''Player:''' If you're such a great witch, get me over!
** '''Winelda:''' See! They pester Winelda!
** '''Player:''' I can do something for you!
** '''Winelda:''' Good! Don't pester! Help!
** '''Winelda:''' Get Winelda 20 limpwurt roots for my pot.
** '''Winelda:''' Then we shows them some magic!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Yes I do!}}
** '''Player:''' Yes I do!
** {{tact|Continues above from "I'm knowing some magic trickesses! I could get over easy as that!"}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Winelda again===
* {{tcond|If the player has no limpwurt roots:}}
** '''Winelda:''' Have you got roots for poor Winelda?
** '''Player:''' How many did you need again?
** '''Winelda:''' We needs 20 Limpwurt roots for pot.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has 1-19 limpwurt roots:}}
** '''Winelda:''' Have you got roots for poor Winelda?
** '''Player:''' I've got some limpwurt roots!
** '''Winelda:''' We needs 20 rooteses!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has 20 limpwurt roots:}}
** '''Player:''' I've got you the limpwurt roots!
** '''Winelda:''' Good! Good! My potion is nearly ready! Bubble, bubble, toil and trouble!
** '''Winelda:''' Now we shows them ours magic! Hold on tight!
** {{tact|Winelda takes the limpwurt roots and teleports the player across the lava.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Winelda after giving the limpwurts===
* '''Player:''' Hi again. Could you do the honours again please?
* '''Winelda:''' Certainly! We helps those that helps poor Winelda!
* {{tact|Winelda teleports the player across the lava.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to a Guardian of Armadyl while wearing the pendant of lucien===
* '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Thou is a foul agent of Lucien! Such an agent must die!
* {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}

===Talking to a Guardian of Armadyl while not wearing the pendant of lucien===
* '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Thou hast ventured deep into the tunnels, you have reached the temple of our master. It is many ages since a pilgrim has come here.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I seek the Staff of Armadyl.}}
** '''Player:''' I seek the Staff of Armadyl.
** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' We are the guardians of the staff, our fathers were guardians and our fathers' fathers before that. Why dost thou seek it?
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Lucien will give me a grand reward for it!}}
*** '''Player:''' Lucien will give me a grand reward for it!
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Thou art working for that spawn of evil?! Fool! You must be cleansed to save your soul!
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|How dare you call me a fool!}}
**** '''Player:''' How dare you call me a fool! I will work for whom I want!
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' We must cleanse the temple!
**** {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}
*** {{topt|I just thought of something I must do!}}
**** '''Player:''' I just thought of something I must do!
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' An agent of evil cannot be allowed to leave!
**** {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}
*** {{topt|You're right, it's time for my yearly bath.}}
**** '''Player:''' You're right, it's time for my yearly bath.
**** {{tbox|The guardian splashes holy water over you.}}
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' You have been cleansed!
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Lucien must not get hold of the staff! He would become too powerful!
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Hast thou come across the undead necromancer? It was he that raised an army of the undead against Varrock a generation ago. If you know where he is you can help us defeat him.
**** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
**** {{topt|Ok! I'll help!}}
***** '''Player:''' Ok! I'll help!
***** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' So he is close by?
***** '''Player:''' Yes!
***** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' He must be gaining in power again. If you can defeat him he will be banished from this plane for a while. You will need this pendant to attack him.
***** {{tbox|pic=Armadyl pendant detail.png|The guardian has given you a pendant.}}{{^|Drops to floor on full inventory}}
***** {{tact|end}}
**** {{topt|No! I shall not turn against my employer!}}
***** '''Player:''' No! I shall not turn against my employer!
***** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Fool! You will die for your sins!
***** {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}
**** {{topt|I need time to think.}}
***** '''Player:''' I need time to think.
***** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Linger a while and be at peace.
***** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Give it to me!}}
*** '''Player:''' Give it to me!
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' The staff is sacred! You will not have it!
*** {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}
** {{topt|I collect rare and powerful artefacts.}}
*** '''Player:''' I collect rare and powerful artefacts.
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Your worldly greed has darkened your soul!
*** {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}
* {{topt|Out of my way fool!}}
** '''Player:''' Out of my way fool!
** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' I may be a fool but I will not step aside!
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Why not?!}}
*** '''Player:''' Why not?!
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Only members of our order are allowed to handle the staff.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Then you must die!}}
*** '''Player:''' Then you must die!
*** {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}
** {{topt|You're right, I will go now.}}
*** '''Player:''' You're right, I will go now.
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' That is a wise decision. Stay a while and let your soul be cleansed!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|What are your kind and what are you doing here?}}
** '''Player:''' What are your kind and what are you doing here?
** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' We are the Guardians of Armadyl. We have kept the temple safe for many ages. The evil in the dungeons seek what lies here. The Mahjarrat are the worst.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|What is the Armadyl?}}
*** '''Player:''' What is the Armadyl?
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Armadyl is the god we serve. We have been charged with guarding his sacred arctifacts until he requires them.
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|Ah ok, thanks.}}
**** '''Player:''' Ah ok, thanks.
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Go in peace.
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{topt|Someone told me there were only three gods.}}
**** '''Player:''' Someone told me there were only three gods. Saradomin, Zamorak and Guthix.
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Saradominists. Bleh. They only acknowledge those three. There are at least twenty gods!
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Who are the Mahjarrat?}}
*** '''Player:''' Who are the Mahjarrat?
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' They are ancient and powerful beings! They are very evil! It is said that they once dominated this plane of existence, Zamorak was supposedly of their blood. They are far fewer in number now.
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Some still have presence in this world in their liche forms. Mahjarrat such as Lucien and Azzanadra would become very powerful if they came into possession of the Staff of Armadyl.
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|Did you say Lucien?}}
**** '''Player:''' Did you say Lucien? It was Lucien that asked me to get the staff!
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' You are a fool to be working for Lucien! Your soul must be cleansed to save you!
**** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
**** {{topt|How dare you call me a fool!}}
***** {{tact|above}}
**** {{topt|I just thought of something I must do!}}
***** {{tact|above}}
**** {{topt|You're right, it's time for my yearly bath.}}
***** {{tact|above}}
*** {{topt|I hope you're doing a good job then!}}
**** '''Player:''' I hope you're doing a good job then!
**** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Do not fear! We are devoted to our charge!
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Wow! You must be really old!}}
*** '''Player:''' Wow! You must be really old!
*** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' No! I am not old! My family has guarded the staff for many generations.
*** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to a Guardian of Armadyl while carrying the staff of Armadyl===
* '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Halt! You will not leave here with the Staff of Armadyl!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the Guardian of Armadyl after agreeing to kill Lucien===
* '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Have you killed Lucien?
* {{tcond|If the player lost the Armadyl pendant:}}
** '''Player:''' Not yet, I've lost the pendant you gave me!
** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Hurry friend! Time is against us!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player still has the Armadyl pendant:}}
** '''Player:''' Not yet.
** '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' Hurry friend! Time is against us!
** {{tact|end}}

===Taking the Staff of armadyl after agreeing to kill Lucien===
* {{mes|You decide not to steal the staff as you have agreed to help the Guardians.}}

===Taking the Staff of armadyl while helping Lucien===
* '''Guardian of Armadyl:''' {{overhead|That is not thine to take!}}
* {{tact|The guardian attacks the player.}}

==Finishing up==
===Talking to Lucien near Varrock===
* '''Lucien:''' Have you got the Staff of Armadyl yet?
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the staff:}}
** '''Player:''' No, not yet.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has the staff:}}
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Yes! Here it is.}}
*** '''Player:''' Yes! Here it is.
*** {{tbox|pic=Staff of armadyl detail.png|You give Lucien the Staff of Armadyl.}}
*** '''Lucien:''' Muhahahhahahaha!
*** '''Lucien:''' I can feel the power of the staff running through me! I will be more powerful and they shall bow down to me!
*** '''Lucien:''' I suppose you want your reward? I shall grant you much power!
*** {{qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}
** {{topt|No, not yet.}}
*** '''Player:''' No, not yet.
*** {{tact|end}}

===Attacking Lucien without wearing the Armadyl pendant===
* '''Lucien:''' You don't want to attack me. I am your friend.
* {{tact|Lucien waves his hand.}}
* {{tbox|You decide not to attack Lucien. He is your friend.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Killing Lucien===
* '''Lucien:''' You have defeated me for now! I shall reappear in the North!
* {{qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}
